# Keep the Braintrailz trail current

`aristotle/references/braintrailz.md` is the trail map for this skill — why decisions were made, not a changelog or session transcript.

When building or changing this project:

- After a durable design choice (architecture, contribution model, versioning, guardrails, packaging), add or update a short section in `braintrailz.md`
- Capture the *why* and the test for the decision; skip back-and-forth and housekeeping detail
- Match the existing voice: trail markers, reusable patterns, no fence
- If `aristotle/` source changed in a way that should ship, rebuild `aristotle.skill` (zip of `aristotle/`)

Do not dump full conversations into the trail. Prefer one tight section per decision.
